title: Default arena is locked??
body: I'm not sure why, but my default arena is locked.  Considering it's the one everyone starts off with, I don't know how that's possible.  Is this true for anyone else, or is it a bug for just me?

replies.body: I have it locked as well.
Locked for me as well. Must be a bug. :/
Yup all ppl have it locked, just noticed it.
